    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"387244\">@Ya√´l Dillies</span> Do you have some draft? I have (some versions of the) strict Jensen inequality in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib/pull/11552\">#11552</a> and I would prefer to have a typeclass saying \"norm is strictly convex\".</p>",
