    {
        "content": "<p>I shouldn't formalize things after midnight: clearly, <code>norm</code> is not a strictly convex function on <code>complex</code> (take <code>x = 1</code>, <code>y = 2</code>, any <code>a</code>, <code>b</code>)</p>",
